{"tid":696472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚嬲 係gym房遇到個仆街大隻佬","createTime":"2018-06-10T06:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T00:55:33.000Z","uid":12883,"like":14,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f90e18d68dbd97d6e331a9a9e0faa1a0562557c8","tid":696472,"uid":12883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟今日如常去做gym 要練腹肌識女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住見到個大隻仔（同rock差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n見佢推緊胸 推到非常掙扎<br />\n都知佢為左威 做啲自己做唔到嘅重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚不自量力<br />\n講真 我都幾驚佢整親 諗緊洗唔洗幫手<br />\n<br />\n屌 點知佢口upup講 come on<br />\n我見身邊無人理佢 咪走去幫佢上<br />\n<br />\n雖然重撚到仆街 但都勉強上到<br />\n我都俾面讚左句 good job bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 佢突然扔低個啞鈴 起身屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好心著雷劈<br />\n呼籲各位健身手足唔好隨便幫人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同大陸啲呀婆差唔多 扶佢變左自己受害<br />\n<br />\n見到post果位人兄 係你呀仆街<br />\n我而加屌撚死你呀"},{"pid":"9b6477d808aca360d19a489e0f72f1a209603be8","tid":696472,"uid":48006,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n小弟今日如常去做gym 要練腹肌識女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住見到個大隻仔（同rock差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n見佢推緊胸 推到非常掙扎<br />\n都知佢為左威 做啲自己做唔到嘅重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n